"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/aD6MpMkcW0ZOlpym7nzLS.png?height=1080&width=1920)\\n\\nHo Ho Ho Ninjas! ü•∑\\n\\nAs the holiday seasonüéÑ is fast approaching, we are thrilled to share some updates with Ninja fam! Along with the rapid growth of NinjaDAOs, a democratized community is shaping the P2E world, contributed by each one of you - thank you for all the support from our managers and scholars! The developing team is sparing no effort for a better Ninja experience:\\n\\n# Product Progress\\n\\n* Scholarship can now be automatically extended if manager and scholar both click ‚ÄúRenew‚Äù button:\\n  * Payment will still be made based on each cycle of offer period\\n  * For managers, please remember to deposit your scholarship on time\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/lW-Rw8F0zII9LyWTo2wHE.png?height=438&width=846)\\n\\n* Scholar profile now reflects real performance statistics on their past scholarships.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Rz1i5WUlFj9673J50uCF3.png?height=250&width=851)\\n\\n* We add review process to all new scholarships and scholars:\\n  * Scholarship will be reviewed for its validity before publication.\\n  * Scholars‚Äô identity will be reviewed before they can apply scholarships. Personal information will be kept safe and never exposed to the pulbic.\\n* We enforce restrictions on scholarships to obey the Axie world rules:\\n  * Each verified scholar could take only one scholarship.\\n  * Scholarship under 700 MMR will be automatically terminated, scholar will receive credit deduction.\\n\\n# Related Links‚Äå\\n\\nFollow our Twitter:¬†<https://twitter.com/NinjaDAOs>\\n\\nJoin our Discord:¬†<https://discord.gg/Kpsk9tWXS4>\\n\\nVisit our Website:¬†[app.ninjadaos.com](https://app.ninjadaos.com/)\\n\\nRead our Docs:¬†[https://ninjadaos.notion.site/NinjaDAOs-WiKi-e6709296d97445b988a3bb87b552e3f9](https://www.notion.so/NinjaDAOs-WiKi-e6709296d97445b9